value: One brings the other a book to read!\nWhat could the story be about...
So engrossed, the two quarrel over it.\nAnd in the end, no one gets the book.
It's a romantic love story! Aww...\nTheir hearts burst with emotion.
It was only the hook! They keep on...\nuntil time and awareness elude them.
$aFoes grant 5x SP for the next $a0,\nand then 2x SP thereafter! (Only highest\nvalue applied. Does not stack.)
